    "collapsible_content_7hCc4P": {
      "type": "collapsible-content",
      "blocks": {
        "collapsible_tab_kmGwGW": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Does the Honiture V8 Pro robot vacuum cleaner have both sweeping and mopping capabilities? What is its maximum suction power?",
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>Yes, the Honiture V8 Pro is a three-in-one robot vacuumer that sweeps, mops, and vacuums. With a maximum suction power of 5,000Pa and four adjustable levels, it easily handles pet hair and deep-seated dirt on carpets and hardwood floors.<\/p>",
            "page": "",
            "custom_liquid": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_8GzHpF": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What technology does the Honiture V8 Pro use for navigation and mapping? Does it support multi-story homes?",
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>The V8 Pro utilizes advanced 5.0 LiDAR (laser radar) navigation technology and SLAM radar navigation. It supports intelligent map storage for up to five floors, making it ideal for multi-story homes without the need for repeated re-mapping.<\/p>",
            "page": "",
            "custom_liquid": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_MmPFjX": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How do I control the Honiture V8 Pro via the app? Can I set restricted areas or custom cleaning zones?",
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>Users can fully control the V8 Pro through the intuitive app. You can design personalized cleaning maps and plans in the app, and set custom No-Go Zones to protect specific areas (such as pet areas).<\/p>",
            "page": "",
            "custom_liquid": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_XVp7Hf": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Does the Honiture V8 Pro have any special enhancements for carpet cleaning?",
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>Yes, the V8 Pro features Carpet Auto-Boost. When the robot detects carpet, it automatically adjusts suction power to maximum level, ensuring thorough cleaning of dust and debris deep inside the carpet.<\/p>",
            "page": "",
            "custom_liquid": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_qRjQbq": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What happens if the Honiture V8 Pro runs out of battery while cleaning a large area?",
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>The Honiture V8 Pro features an automatic recharge and resume feature. When the battery runs low, the robot automatically returns to its charging station. Once the battery is restored, it automatically returns to where it left off and continues cleaning.<\/p>",
            "page": "",
            "custom_liquid": ""
          }
        }
      },
